# hexa-lang /.raw — L0 universal rules (parser-owner self-host)
# SSOT — 이 파일이 hexa-lang 의 root SSOT.
# 포맷 스펙: self/raw_loader.hexa (이 repo 가 owner)
# 검증: ./build/hexa_stage0 self/raw_cli.hexa verify
#
# 포맷:
#   raw <num> <status> "<name>"
#     <key> <value...>
#     ...
#   (빈 줄 = rule 구분, # = 주석, 같은 key 여러 줄 = 배열)
#
# 모든 hive .raw rules 를 inherit (cross-repo self-format#inherit) — 이 파일은 hexa-lang local 만 선언.

raw 1 live "hexa-lang self-host fixpoint — parser-owner consumes own format"
  slug hexa-lang-self-host
  enforce self/raw_cli.hexa verify
  decl self/raw_loader.hexa
  scope hexa-lang/.raw + hexa-lang/.own + hexa-lang/.doc
  why hexa-lang implements raw_loader.hexa — the parser FOR self-format DSL. Hosting zero canonical .raw at root = meta-circular violation. raw_loader.hexa MUST round-trip parse this file as the implementation acceptance test.
  proof self/raw_cli.hexa verify --target hexa-lang/.raw
  proof self/raw_cli.hexa verify --target hexa-lang/.own
  proof self/raw_cli.hexa verify --target hexa-lang/.doc
  severity block

raw 2 live "naming reconciliation — .commands → .command (canonical)"
  slug naming-canonical
  status convention
  scope .commands → .command, .chain (chain-kind extension), .raw-ref (sync metadata)
  why hexa-lang invented .commands (plural) before canonical .command (singular) was promoted across hive. Reconciliation deferred until consumers (tool/cmd_*.hexa handlers) are repointed.
  defer-until phase-3 of F1 bootstrap (after .raw + .own + .doc land)
  follow-up rename .commands → .command + update tool/install_os.hexa references
  promoted-at 2026-04-26 (rename landed: .commands → .command, 11 cross-refs migrated)
  severity warn

raw 3 convention "follower-repo .raw-ref pattern — canonical mirror pin"
  slug raw-ref-follower
  enforce tool/raw_sync.hexa
  decl .raw-ref
  scope follower repos mirroring hexa-lang canonical .raw (contact, papers, anima, n6-architecture, nexus, void, airgenome, hexa-os)
  format ref <N> <status> "<label>" + source + branch + path + pinned-hash + checked-at
  why follower repos pin to hexa-lang canonical .raw via .raw-ref. tool/raw_sync.hexa populates pinned-hash + checked-at; drift detection at sync time. hexa-lang itself is the canonical owner (no .raw-ref at root).
  proof tool/raw_sync.hexa check
  severity warn

raw 100 live "anima-local: raw 9 hexa-only scope override + grandfather list"
  slug anima-hexa-only-scope
  base raw 9 hexa-only
  since 2026-04-26 (ω-rules P4 Phase 0+1)
  scope anima git-tracked source dirs ONLY (excludes vendor + archive + jurisdiction-out)
  opt-out ready/ — historical corpus archive, .gitignore'd; raw 9 jurisdiction-out (1431 files)
  opt-out .claude/ — Claude Code internal hooks/settings; vendor (1045 files)
  opt-out .raw-audit/ — append-only audit ledger (raw 77 separate format)
  opt-out node_modules/ build/ dist/ checkpoints/ data/ — vendor + build + checkpoint outputs
  exempt-via-gitignore tool/p_s_projector_proto.py — UPSTREAM-BLOCKED on numpy stdlib in hexa (linalg.svd / norm / bincount; multi-month port). raw#9 PARTIAL-RELAXED per file header. .gitignore'd via `**/*.py` rule 2026-04-26 (`git rm --cached`); output cert state/p_s_projector_proto_r{6,8}.json IS the SSOT.
  retired-2026-04-26 tool/an11_c_jsd_h_last.py — Phase 5: ported to tool/an11_c_jsd_h_last.hexa (hexa-native, jq + awk), 6-digit numerical equivalence verified vs .py baseline (mean_jsd_bits 0.110477 vs 0.11047673814646303, all 16 per-prompt diffs < 1e-6). .py removed from disk after `git rm --cached` had already gitignored it.
  exempt-via-gitignore tool/active_redteam_dEF_proto.py + tool/active_redteam_prototype.py — .gitignore'd Python research harness (raw 9 explicit relaxation per file headers); honored by canonical lint via `git ls-files --others --exclude-standard`
  retired-2026-04-26 anima-speak/experiments/piper_v2gen.sh — `git rm` (replaced by piper_v2gen.hexa Phase 4 port)
  retired-2026-04-26 anima-speak/experiments/yt_kor_corpus_fetch.sh — `git rm` (replaced by yt_kor_corpus_fetch.hexa Phase 4 port)
  retired-2026-04-26 anima-speak/experiments/ab_metrics.sh — `git rm` (replaced by ab_metrics.hexa Phase 4 port)
  retired-2026-04-26 anima-speak/experiments/build_tts_dataset.sh — `git rm` (replaced by build_tts_dataset.hexa Phase 4 port)
  retired-2026-04-26 anima-speak/experiments/corpus_pipeline_full.sh — `git rm` (replaced by corpus_pipeline_full.hexa Phase 4 port)
  retired-2026-04-26 anima-speak/experiments/piper_ab_gen.sh — `git rm` (full .hexa companion at piper_ab_gen.hexa 449L)
  retired-2026-04-26 anima-agent/pyproject.toml — `git rm` (Dockerfile mandates "no python/cargo single-binary hexa runtime"; documented retire decision in docs/anima_agent_restructure_plan_20260419.md "삭제 (R37)")
  retired-2026-04-26 training/archive/launchers_alm_py_legacy_20260416/launch_*.sh (5) — Phase 1a `git rm` clear retire (already in archive/ + _legacy_ + dated)
  why anima CLAUDE.md declared hexa-only but enforcement scope was implicit. ω-rules R9.1 raw count 2494 의 99.3% (ready/1431 + .claude/1045) 는 jurisdiction-out. 실제 active source 위반 16 (P0 baseline) → 11 (Phase 1a: 5 archive launchers) → 9 (Phase 3: piper_ab_gen.sh + pyproject.toml) → 0 (Phase 4: 5 .sh ported + 2 .py reclassified gitignored-exempt 2026-04-26). raw 9 hexa-only 100% achievement under canonical lint.
  proof /Users/ghost/core/hive/tool/hexa_only_lint.hexa --root /Users/ghost/core/anima
  proof-expected-output raw#9 (--root /Users/ghost/core/anima): untracked 위반 없음 — pass (exit=0)
  follow-up Phase 5 (optional): port an11_c_jsd_h_last.py → .hexa (lift exempt-via-gitignore → fully hexa-native; ~1일 with jq+awk math) / hexa-lang stdlib upstream: numpy SVD equivalent (multi-month) + subprocess UX polish (some 5 .hexa scripts use awk for log/sqrt math)
